00:29:21.360 --> 00:29:23.520
U mom životu ovih dana,

00:29:23.600 --> 00:29:26.800
milioni na prema jedan
čini se kao dobri izgledi.

00:30:02.560 --> 00:30:04.240
Izdajica!

00:30:05.040 --> 00:30:06.880
Gotov si.

00:30:20.080 --> 00:30:22.080
Ti seronjo!

00:31:36.720 --> 00:31:39.040
Aksone?
-Nina?

00:31:39.120 --> 00:31:42.160
