00:33:52.480 --> 00:33:55.200
Došao sam, moj zadatak...

00:33:55.280 --> 00:33:58.320
Ne razumijem...

00:34:01.200 --> 00:34:02.640
Moramo da idemo.

00:34:02.720 --> 00:34:05.280
Ok, moramo da idemo,
moramo da idemo, odmah.

00:34:16.240 --> 00:34:17.760
Stepenice!

00:34:24.160 --> 00:34:26.560
Idemo, idemo!

00:34:38.240 --> 00:34:40.000
Hajde!

00:34:43.360 --> 00:34:45.120
Požuri!

00:34:49.680 --> 00:34:51.440
Idemo!

00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:55.760
Sagni se!
-Ubi je.

00:35:04.160 --> 00:35:07.160
Jesi li dobro?
-Nemoj da brineš za mene.

00:35:09.120 --> 00:35:10.960
Uhvatite ovo šupci!

00:35:16.800 --> 00:35:18.560
Pokrivaj me!

00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:52.160
Nina!

00:35:53.360 --> 00:35:55.160
Nina!

00:36:00.240 --> 00:36:03.920
Nina! Nina!

00:36:13.440 --> 00:36:15.200
Hajde! Hajde.

00:36:21.040 --> 00:36:22.560
Hajde.

00:37:00.800 --> 00:37:04.400
Jesi li dobro?
-Moje jebeno koljeno!

00:37:04.480 --> 00:37:07.360
Moramo se negdje sakriti.
Gdje ćemo? -Kod mene.

00:37:37.840 --> 00:37:40.560
<i>Pobrinite se da dođete
sa osmijehom na posao danas</i>

00:37:40.680 --> 00:37:43.840
<i>i budite ponosni što ste dio države.</i>

00:37:44.000 --> 00:37:46.400
<i>Svi ste bitni.</i>

00:38:03.920 --> 00:38:07.360
<i>Ovo je važna poruka za javnost.
Upozorenje za sve vas.</i>

00:38:07.520 --> 00:38:09.440
<i>Ovi za sada ne
identifikovani teroristi</i>

00:38:09.440 --> 00:38:11.280
